import {
  Container,
  Divider,
  Paper,
  Typography,
  Box,
  Grid,
  Card,
  CardMedia,
  TextField,
} from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";
import { styles } from "./styles";
const AddPostPage = () => {
  return (
    <Container sx={{ paddingTop: 5, paddingLeft: 2 }}>
      <Typography sx={{ fontSize: 20 }}>Add Post</Typography>
      <Paper elevation={3} sx={styles.container}>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
          <Grid item sm={4}>
            <Card sx={{ height: "100%" }}>
              <CardMedia
                height={194}
                component={"img"}
                sx={{
                  backgroundColor: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)",
                  backgroundBlendMode: "darken",
                }}
                image="https://www.history.com/.image/ar_4:3%2Cc_fill%2Ccs_srgb%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto:good%2Cw_1200/MTU3ODc5MDg2NDMyNjU5MTY3/morning-light-on-4.jpg"
                title="image"
              />
            </Card>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item sm={4}>
            <TextField
              name="adventureName"
              label="Adventure Name"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              autoFocus
              type="text"
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item sm={4}>
            <TextField
              name="adventureTags"
              label="Tags"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              type="text"
            />
          </Grid>
          <Grid item sm={8}>
            <TextField
              name="adventureDetails"
              label="Adventure Details"
              fullWidth
              variant="outlined"
              type="text"
              multiline
            />
          </Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Paper>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default AddPostPage;
